You can learn more about craft by reading <a href="https://github.com/MasoniteFramework/docs/tree/ba9d9f8ac3e41d58b9d92d951f92c898fb16a2a4/the-craft-command.md">The Craft Command</a> documentation or continue on to learning about how to create web application by first reading the <a href="the-basics/routing.md">Routing </a>documentation
{% endhint %}
